  "title": "Prime Mover Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct pre-operational checks on prime mover and chassis before executing job operation</li>\n  <li>Ensure that the vehicle is in good condition for delivery &amp; collection of containers and loose cargoes on timely</li>\n  <li>To adhere and to abide with all Singapore ports, shipyards and road safety rules and regulations</li>\n  <li>Report vehicle issues &amp; accident to Controller</li>\n  <li>Follow job orders given by Controller</li>\n  <li>Transport containers and loose cargoes according to the assigned schedule</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Primary or Secondary school education</li>\n  <li>Able to understand basic English</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of working experience as Prime Mover Driver</li>\n  <li>Possess Class 4 or 5 license</li>\n  <li>Good driving record with no traffic violation</li>\n  <li>Able to start work immediately or short notice</li>\n</ul>",
